3.1 RFCs (Request for Comments)
DNS (Base del Sistema de Nombres de Dominio)

Mockapetris, P. (1987).
RFC 1034 – Domain Names: Concepts and Facilities.
https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/rfc1034/

Mockapetris, P. (1987).
RFC 1035 – Domain Names: Implementation and Specification.
https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/rfc1035/

DNSSEC (Especificaciones principales)

Arends, R., et al. (2005).
RFC 4033 – DNS Security Introduction and Requirements.
https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/rfc4033/

Arends, R., et al. (2005).
RFC 4034 – Resource Records for DNS Security Extensions.
https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/rfc4034/

Arends, R., et al. (2005).
RFC 4035 – Protocol Modifications for DNSSEC.
https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/rfc4035/

Complementos y actualizaciones relevantes

Laurie, B., et al. (2008).
RFC 5155 – DNSSEC Hashed Authenticated Denial of Existence (NSEC3).
https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/rfc5155/

D. J. Bernstein, et al. (2012).
RFC 5702 – Use of SHA-2 Algorithms with RSA in DNSKEY and RRSIG.
https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/rfc5702/

IETF DNSOP Working Group (documentos varios).
Página de trabajos y drafts en curso:
https://datatracker.ietf.org/wg/dnsop/documents/

